            "chapterTitle": "Condemnation of Pride and Self-Conceit",
            "urn": 1606100,
            "body": "<p>Abu Hurairah (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) said, \"There are three (types of) people to whom Allah will not speak on the Day of Resurrection, nor will He purify them, nor look at them, and they will have a painful punishment. These are: An aged man who commits Zina (illicit sexual act), a ruler who lies, and a proud poor person.\"<br/><br/><b>[Muslim]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
            "grades": []
        },
